      <title>总理辞职后，暴力破坏了塞尔维亚议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/violence-disrupts-serbia-parliament-after-prime-minister-resigns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反对派代表在塞尔维亚国民议会中投掷了烟手榴弹，破坏了一场会议，确认了总理米洛斯·沃切维奇（Milos Vucevic）的辞职，并就旨在缓解巴尔干国家的反政府抗议活动的法律进行了辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/violence-disrupts-serbia-parliament-after-prime-minister-resigns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 11:42:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
