    <item>
      <title>特朗普国家讲话在价格恐惧的情况下测试经济信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-speech-to-congress-economy-tariffs-ukraine-on-agenda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的黄金时段地址周二晚上来自国会大厦山（Capitol Hill＆Mdash）被称为“美国梦的更新”的编年史；在第二任期初期，正处于关键时刻，当选他以应对通货膨胀和改善经济的选民开始权衡其议程的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-speech-to-congress-economy-tariffs-ukraine-on-agenda</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟提出了1500亿欧元的国防贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/eu-proposes-150-billion-in-loans-for-pan-european-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将提议延长1500亿欧元（1580亿美元）的贷款，以提高国防支出，因为该集团试图适应美国总统唐纳德·特朗普突然在美国大陆上对美国安全的撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/eu-proposes-150-billion-in-loans-for-pan-european-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 08:34:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国报复，美国主要的美国农业出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-puts-tariffs-on-us-soybean-corn-agricultural-commodities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为对华盛顿的对策的一部分，中国将向美国农产品征收关税，威胁要破坏两个农业强国之间的主要贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-puts-tariffs-on-us-soybean-corn-agricultural-commodities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级了全球贸易战，引发了卖山雀的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加了他对加拿大和墨西哥的威胁，并以全面的进口征税征收，并对中国的现有指控增加了一倍，这激发了迅速报复，这使世界经济陷入了深入的贸易战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
